      *              * cancellazione                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           set       w-rap-ele-inx        to   1                      .
           search    w-rap-ele-prf
                     when   w-rap-sts-prf
                           (w-rap-ele-inx)
                                          =    09
                     go to can-prf-sel-100.
