      *              * Se almeno un elemento trovato                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scansione per determinare quanti sono gli   *
      *                  * elementi da cancellare                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-rap-c01-prf          .
           move      zero                 to   w-rap-c02-prf          .
       can-prf-sel-120.
           add       1                    to   w-rap-c01-prf          .
           if        w-rap-c01-prf        >    w-rap-num-prf
                     go to can-prf-sel-200.
           if        w-rap-sts-prf
                    (w-rap-c01-prf)       =    09
                     add  1               to   w-rap-c02-prf          .
           go to     can-prf-sel-120.
       can-prf-sel-200.
