      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Box vuoto                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      10                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      75                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
