      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-exe-stp-ora-ini    to   pfc-ora-ius            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data fine ultima stampa                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-exe-stp-dat-fin    to   pfc-dat-fus            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ora fine ultima stampa                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-exe-stp-ora-fin    to   pfc-ora-fus            .
